title: Maoz Falafel - Muntplein
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Mediterranean, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out
description: Part of an international falafel fast food chain. This one sits between the Amstel and the Reguliersbreestraat -- from the Central Station, take tram 4, 9, 16, 24 or 25, and get off at the Muntplein, walk towards the Muntplein, MAOZ is located on the left side of the square.
